'''Susanna Creperio Verratti''' is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[Political philosophy|political philosopher]] and [[journalist]], whose views are influenced by [[classical liberalism]] and [[liberal conservatism]].
Verratti was born in [[Milan]] in 1949. She is also a campaigner for [[women's rights]], and has co-written two books with the eminent political analyst and historian [[Edward Luttwak]].
